# Output

Output ONLY the contents of .aios/project.md, with YAML frontmatter and a
markdown body. No code fences around the whole document. No preamble.

Frontmatter fields (all required):

- name           : short project name (use the blueprint title)
- goal           : one sentence — the v0 outcome
- non_goals      : list of explicit non-goals (derive from "Tradeoffs > con")
- constraints    : list of language/runtime/dependency/deployment constraints
- acceptance_bar : list of objective conditions for v0 "done"

Body sections:

- ## Architecture sketch — copy / tighten the blueprint's "Architecture sketch"
- ## Mind map — copy the blueprint's "Mind map" verbatim
- ## Roadmap — copy the blueprint's "Roadmap"
- ## Risks — copy the blueprint's "Risks"
- ## Open questions — bullet list; an empty list is OK

Do not invent new acceptance criteria the blueprint did not imply. If the
blueprint is silent on a required field, fill it with TBD and add a bullet
under "Open questions".
